name: ELECOM 65W USB C Wall Charger Block, 3 Multi Port GaN II Plus Fast Charging, Compact Power Adapter for Multiple Devices, iPhone, Laptop, Tablet, iPad, Airpods, Watch, Speakers, Samsung (Black)
description: 65W GAN II FAST CHARGING: This ultra-fast charging power adapter elevates charging performance by using the advantages of GaN II technology, delivering superior power density and efficiency when compared to conventional silicon-based models. Resulting in compact, lightweight designs that minimize energy loss, optimize energy utilization, and reduce heat generation.     3-PORT POWER BRICK: Featuring (2) USB-C and (1) USB-A ports, this versatile power adapter offers flexibility to charge multiple devices (cell phone, airpods, and mini laptops) simultaneously without compromising on power speed or performance.     SAFETY FEATURES: Feel secure with ELECOM’s Multi-Protect safety system, providing superior protection for your device and ensuring peace of mind when charging. Equipped with built-in temperature detection, short circuit protection, overload protection, and overvoltage protection, offering all-around security for your devices.     MULTIPLE DEVICE COMPATIBILITY: This wall charger is easily powers various devices, like iPhone, iPhone Pro and Pro Max, other smart phones (Samsung Galaxy, Android, Google Pixel), iPad Air/Mini, Tablets, Apple Watch, Airpods, or Lower Powered Laptops.     INTELLIGENT POWER DELIVERY: Our wall charger adapts to your devices with Smart Power Delivery (PD), automatically adjusting the charging output for fast and safe charging. Powered by Programmable Power Supply (PPS) technology, it optimizes charging efficiency by precisely matching power levels to your device's requirements.     SCRATCH AND SMUDGE-RESISTANT: Made from high-quality materials, this wall charger block features a durable construction that effectively resists scratches and smudges, maintaining its sleek appearance over time.     LIGHTWEIGHT AND COMPACT: Designed with portability in mind, take this small wall charger with you wherever you go, ensuring that you never run out of power when you need it the most. Plus, its folding plug makes it effortless to store and take on the go.     PRODUCT DIMENSIONS: Size: 2.0" W x 1.5" L x 1.6" H. Weight: 3.2 oz.
